Package: pba
Version: 0.2-2
Date: 2011-03-29
Title: Probabilistic Bias Analysis
Author@R: person("Jeremy", "Hetzel", "Thoms",
				 email = "jthetzel@gmail.com")
Author: Jeremy T. Hetzel <jthetzel@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Jeremy T. Hetzel <jthetzel@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.12.0), plyr, ggplot2, QRMlib, reshape
Description: The pba package performs probabilistic bias analyses with methods adapted from Lash TL, Fox MP, and Fink AK's Applying Quantitative Bias Analysis to Epidemiological Data (2010). The package can adjust for multiple sources of misclassification, selection, and unmeasured confounding bias.
License: GPL-3
URL: http://pba.r-forge.r-project.org/
BugReports: https://r-forge.r-project.org/tracker/?func=add&group_id=988&atid=3913		 
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes				 